Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=6}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.26,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.72,0:00:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My decision, and now, \N the resulting state of affairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.22,0:00:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In retrospect, it needed to come to this...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.62,0:00:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to realise you were right all along.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.06,0:00:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you mentioned the importance \Nof bearing responsibility before.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.22,0:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I didn't fully get what you meant \Nby that, but it's finally become clear to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.03,0:00:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not our experiences that matter, \Nbut the choices we make.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.52,0:01:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For all the choice only they can make, \Nadults bear the burden of duty and responsibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.80,0:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's you, an adult I can trust,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.65,0:01:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have faith that your decisions \Ncan pave the way to a different conclusion.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.24,0:01:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Away from the dark, twisted fate that looms before us.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.29,0:01:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.34,0:01:22.29,Default,,0,0,100,,I beg you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.74,0:02:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.00,0:02:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Amidst the General Student Council's turmoil \Nfollowing the President's disappearance,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.74,0:02:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanctum Tower has been re-lit, \Nand administrative functions are back on track.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.01,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Following this, the turmoil throughout the academy city, \NKivotos, is anticipated to slowly diminish.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.96,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Meow{*Nyaa}, {*}meow{*nyaa}, {*}meow{*nyaa}. {## is this a cat website reference?!?!!}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The next stop is Abydos High School.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exiting at the next stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}, are you serious?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.51,0:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.30,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}biked{\i0} to the Abydos industrial district {\i1}and{\i0} back?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hundreds of kilometres!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I've never gotten\Na good look of it before.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It ended up being just the right distance.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy, Shiroko{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do over the weekend, Serika?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was over at the library reading.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You were there too, Serika{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there yesterday, but I didn't see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We must've totally missed each other!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you reading, Ayane{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.71,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do a bit of research on the DOHC \NI came across while doing repairs the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.46,0:04:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, DOHC stands for "Double Overhead Cam".
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a type of engine.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it might come in handy later.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what about you, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Same ol' routine as usual. {ML04: I quite like "old-timer" as loc for Hoshino's 'ojisan' but your call BB. Also I would unloc it for alt track but again uty.}{### I think it's one ofo those cases where we should switch it up on a case-by-case basis, but try not to be TOO explicit if we can help it.} {### Alt: Same ol' routine for an old timer like me. }
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you all had a fun weekend!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Nonomi?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I went shopping!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked up a couple snacks,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,some everyday necessities I was running low on...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.13,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and about forty dumbbells!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.39,0:05:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin with our regular meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.39,0:05:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin, let's discuss the major event \Nrecently covered by the news.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.34,0:05:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The General Student Council, or GSC for short, \Nis tasked with maintaining harmony among the schools
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.15,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in the academy city of Kivotos, under the guidance \Nof the General Student Council President.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.40,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's been reported that the GSC\NPresident went missing a few days ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.58,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident may be what sparked \Nthe recent unrest in various school districts.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.29,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the GSC, what happened \Nwith that {\i1}something{\i0}-treaty?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.50,0:06:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The non-aggression pact between \NTrinity General School and Gehenna Academy?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the Eden Treaty.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the one!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Has that been signed yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.31,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the GSC President who proposed it, \Nbut she's missing now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say what will happen with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, speaking of which, Ayane{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.90,0:06:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss of Shiba Seki Ramen said the Kata-Kata \NHelmet Gang is causing trouble in our district again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.66,0:06:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Their ramen is really good.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you go there often, Shiroko{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On occasion.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.56,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Abydos is getting more \Nand more dangerous as time goes on.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get concerned.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.57,0:06:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to inform the GSC \Nabout our predicament, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.31,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The President has gone missing, \Nso they probably don't have time for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not like we've got time \Nto spare for them, either. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.10,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for choosing Kaiser Loan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.32,0:07:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you'll have paid everything off \Nin 309 years and 2 months!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again next month!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.33,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,309 years and 2 months \Nuntil we've paid off our debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That took longer than expected.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.58,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did I hear that right, punk-ass ladies?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say I have "lame-ass hair"?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare insult my {\i1}glorious pompadour{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, we love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.58,Alt,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.50,0:08:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you got lame-ass hair, \Nwhat else are we gonna call it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doubling down, you punks?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Light 'em up, gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see you talk smack now!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you seriously think...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...your lame-ass bullets...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.54,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...could stop us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're still alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sunbathing?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did you collapse?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Water...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got an energy drink.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a sip?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you saved me there!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}, did you kidnap this man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.43,0:10:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}, have you finally turned to a life of crime?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta cover this up \Nbefore the cops come knocking!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.18,0:10:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he has business with our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's a client?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Abydos was a desert,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.34,0:10:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't anticipate it to be {\i1}this{\i0} hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so dehydrated on the way here, I collapsed.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, if you wouldn't mind,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,could you tell us about yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.78,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a teacher from the \NIndependent Federal Investigation Club, SCHALE.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, so this guy's with the GSC?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.54,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they finally accepted our request for aid!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Ayane{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is! Sending all those requests finally paid off!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.68,0:11:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can get our supplies.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.98,0:11:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note, may I have your attention, everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is this...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.90,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give you this.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.77,0:11:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can start receiving ammunition and supplies!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.06,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we should tell Hoshino{**-senpai} the good news as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably napping in the usual spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go wake her up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.29,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't introduced ourselves yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl just now was Kuromi Serika, a first-year.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Izayoi Nonomi. I'm a second-year!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.66,0:12:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Okusora Ayane. I'm a first-year.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.59,0:12:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sunaookami Shiroko, a second-year.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.74,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was the first to meet you, \Nso I'm sure you already knew that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.06,0:12:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but I'm not trying to hold it against anyone or anything. {### can I get some clarification on this line?}{Not assert dominance - rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.34,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally there's the president of the {Foreclosure }Task Force,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.14,0:12:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.57,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We make up the Abydos High School \NForeclosure Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure's all mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down, Serika{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.96,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor legs aren't what they used to be! 
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit messing around! {### alt: Enough excuses, gra!}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the club president, so act like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Meow meow{*Nyaa nyaa}, I'm Takanashi Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meetcha.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.84,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm a teacher from SCHALE.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you around the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.41,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The desertification has progressed \Nquite a bit around the Abydos district.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.64,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.77,0:13:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The school was already like this back when I enrolled.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.68,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen any other students so far.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.71,0:13:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really just the five of you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's just us.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.34,0:13:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully, this school is in a lot of debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the only ones left.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.51,0:13:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Foreclosure Task Force, \Nwe take on all sorts of requests,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.47,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and we put the rewards towards paying off the debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have it pretty rough.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, everyone cleaned out the gymnasium.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.22,0:14:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayane was sick that day, \Nso it was just the four of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.70,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There was more junk than we thought, \Nso it took a bit longer than expected,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but there weren't any complications.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.50,0:14:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, Ayane got really mad at us.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.49,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an empty room.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.78,0:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free use this room from now on, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The faculty office is full of sand, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it too small?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.49,0:14:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, why do you want to protect this school?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunfire?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, Abydos High School!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.56,0:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the day you finally submit to us!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kata-Kata Helmet Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.92,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all times for them to show up...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.38,0:15:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I can't even take a nap in peace.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, we'll just send 'em \Nrunning home like we always do.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's hurry to the yard!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, stay here and keep your head down.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.59,0:15:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Arona!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.20,0:15:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}, take this.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They just won't give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.55,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running low on ammunition.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If they had showed up just a bit later, \Nwe'd have restocked, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an issue.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.66,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up already!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.05,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you're almost outta bullets!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.73,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Where did they get that information?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter, Ayane{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ammo or not, we can take 'em on any day!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta back up Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.19,0:16:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, eat it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not let you have Abydos High School!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}! Nonomi{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.84,0:16:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! We need to regroup!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,These scrubs are all over the place!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.50,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like that tip about their ammo \Nwas right on the money!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to end this once and for all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.07,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get 'em, gang! We almost got 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.86,0:16:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, the Abydos students won't last long like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys hanging in there?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just barely.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stop bunching up. We need to spread out!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, c'mon. Still not giving up?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.91,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you can't beat us.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just getting started!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. At this rate, they'll overwhelm us!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.27,0:17:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I can't believe \Nwe're about to lose to these jerks!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this chump?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.33,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to protect this school?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this school is the place we belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everyone else feel the same way?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.27,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell do you think you are, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to help these girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.78,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'll have to kindly ask you \Nto leave the school premises.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,First you show up outta nowhere, \Nand now you're bossing us around?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.87,0:18:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn you to Swiss cheese!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.86,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi! Suppressive fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.77,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, take aim!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You ain't gotta tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you do—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.77,0:18:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't let the youngsters steal the show.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Coordinates locked in!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.86,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch, Shiroko{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice timing, Ayane!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.93,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're so tough!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get it together!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.46,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't look!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.49,0:19:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Checkmate!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.33,0:19:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stay away!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, hold on, I s-surrender.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.05,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that hurts! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave already.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.08,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving! We're leaving already!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.06,0:20:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Great work!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.77,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought we'd swing that around.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me? I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.89,0:20:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As a teacher, I just couldn't ignore students in need.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.84,0:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.70,0:20:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have handled those losers on our own.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.05,0:20:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Serika{**-chan}, {*}always gotta be so independent{*still tsundere as always}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just eat you up, Serika{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hide your appreciation.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up already!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.50,0:20:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\t(1926,3928,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Lemme go, Hoshino{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.95,0:20:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1926,3928,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}So this is what having a teacher is like...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.28,0:23:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... Strawberry milk...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.59,0:23:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Arona.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.03,0:23:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{=7}I've been expecting you, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}!

